      "date": "2017-04-06 14:24:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nLooks like sanity-hsm test1_b failed with \"request on 0x200000401:0x8:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1\".  We have seen similar errors with other sanity-hsm tests, but giving that test1b deals with composite files, it is worth digging into to be sure instead of just restarting.   Bobijam, can you have a look?",
